The first of many editions, this map will generate a completely new environment upon every round, thus no two rounds will ever be the same.

MORE UPDATES TO COME!!!

This map will start off a little basic, so as to get things going.

Features 122 objects to place over 320 squares.

A bigger variety of objects will be coming soon.
